data.title: Guinness Open Gate Brewery in Baltimore, MD USA
data.meta_description: Explore Guinness Open Gate Brewery, the first Guinness Brewery in the USA since 1954.
data.text:
The Guinness Open Gate Brewery welcomes guests into our vast indoor and outdoor spaces.

Taproom: Reservations are accepted but are not required for seating in our taproom.

Beer Garden: Seating within our beer garden is on a first come, first served basis (reservations are not required or accepted for this space).
